---
layout: base.njk
title: "Insights & Articles"
description: "Philosophical insights, reflections on Hindu thought, and explorations of ancient wisdom from the author of Core Concepts in Hindu Philosophy."
---

<style>
  .blog-hero {
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    padding: 80px calc(var(--spacing-base) * 4);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .blog-hero h1 {
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-base) * 2);
  }

  .blog-hero p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .blog-posts {
    padding: 80px calc(var(--spacing-base) * 4);
    background-color: #fafbf9;
  }

  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: calc(var(--spacing-base) * 5);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .blog-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,42,74,0.08);
    transition: all 0.35s ease;
  }

  .blog-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  }

  .blog-card-body {
    padding: calc(var(--spacing-base) * 5);
  }

  .blog-card-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-base) * 2);
  }

  .blog-card h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-base) * 2);
  }

  .blog-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-base) * 4);
  }

  .blog-card a {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    transition: gap 0.35s ease;
  }

  .blog-card a:hover {
    gap: 10px;
  }
</style>

<section class="blog-hero">
  <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--secondary-color);">Reflections & Insights</span>
  <h1>Philosophical Articles</h1>
  <p>Explorations of Hindu philosophy's core concepts, context, and contemporary relevance.</p>
</section>

<section class="blog-posts">
  {% if collections.blog.length %}
  <div class="blog-grid">
    {% for post in collections.blog %}
    <article class="blog-card" data-scroll-reveal>
      <div class="blog-card-body">
        <div class="blog-card-meta">{{ post.data.date | dateFormat }}</div>
        <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">Read more →</a>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <div style="text-align: center; padding: 80px 0; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <span class="eyebrow">Coming Soon</span>
    <h2 style="margin-top: 16px;">Articles in Progress</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--text-light); margin-top: 16px;">In-depth essays on Vedanta, karma, dharma, and the philosophical traditions of ancient India are being prepared. Check back soon.</p>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</section>
